  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="spec FR-20">Deploy-Playbook.ps1 writes node.sprk_executortype explicitly; no name-detection; no `__actionType` injection. This task documents the new behavior.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec FR-28">UPDATE in place. No SUPERSEDED markers, no "(removed — see X)" leave-behinds.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-08">Documentation discipline.</constraint>
    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §11">Cost-of-doing-nothing: maker following the old recipe would be confused why the workaround steps don't apply (and might try to manually inject `__actionType` against a script that now lints-reject it).</constraint>
